<li><a href="/wiki/Elmo_Stoll" title="Elmo Stoll">Elmo Stoll</a>, bishop and founder of the "Christian Communities"</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Sanford_Calvin_Yoder" title="Sanford Calvin Yoder">Sanford Calvin Yoder</a>, religious scholar and WWI conscientious objector</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Wes_Yoder" title="Wes Yoder">Wes Yoder</a>, religious advocate</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Tripp_York" title="Tripp York">Tripp York</a>, religious educator</li></ul>
